    &lt;figcaption&gt;
        &lt;h4&gt;Americanium&lt;/h4&gt;
        
    &lt;/figcaption&gt;
    
&lt;/figure&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Cultural news aggregation site with a custom RSS module that enables periodic updates from RSS, twitter, flickr and YouTube feeds.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This product was concieved by 24 Hour Museum journalist Jon Pratty, and used  guardian.com as inspiration for the content design patterns. Built on Drupal, all you do is pick interesting feeds, and the site updates itself!&lt;/p&gt;

