&lt;p&gt;Mousharaka graphic design conference was the first of its kind in Doha. Hired by Virginia Commonwealth University to execute the website for the conference&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We designed dual language interface (Arabic/English), and interfaced with online conference paper manager.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In addition to implementation, I arranged secure hosting for the site.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Menu structures for both English and Arabic content were fine tuned here, to ensure they made sense and provided good wayfinding for both audiences.&lt;/p&gt;

